Client Software Suite for Linux for Use with 
Gigabit Ethernet(GigE) and USB 3.0 Cameras (U3V)
================================================================

System Requirements
===================

GigE
----
A GigE network adapter that supports jumbo frames is recommended. Concerning
performance and reliability we made best experiences with the Intel PRO 1000,
I210 and I350 series.

USB
---
For U3V devices a USB3-capable USB controller is necessary. 


Installation
=============

The installation of Client for Linux is described in the INSTALL text document.


Documentation
=============

The installation includes a "doc" sub-folder containing the
Programmer's Guide and API reference documentation. 


Sample Programs
===============

The installation archive includes a set of sample programs. 
They are located in the "Samples" folder.

